From dfc69a2f8b16c426fe9febd1773c5e6e1844b77e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yang Chen <yang.chen@quantatw.com>
Date: Fri, 7 Feb 2025 15:23:13 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] ARM: dts: aspeed: ventura: modify dts for PVT stage

Modify the DTS of ventura for PVT stage as follow items:
1. Add gpio-led for each tray led control.
2. Remove the power monitor IC defined in DTS because multiple sources
   of the RMC board have the same i2c address.
3. Add 2nd HSC xdp710.

Signed-off-by: Yang Chen <yang.chen@quantatw.com>
---
